sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    box Client
        participant C as MCP client
    end

    box Server
        participant MCP as MCP control plane
        participant HTTP as HTTP data plane
    end

    Note over C,HTTP: (b) TransForm — 1 MCP round trip

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over C,HTTP: MCP RTT 1 — hint, select, deliver
        C->>MCP: fused call
        MCP->>MCP: hint + select + encode
        alt small result
            MCP-->>C: inline JSON
        else large columnar result
            MCP-->>C: descriptor + URL
            C->>HTTP: GET bytes
            HTTP-->>C: Parquet / Arrow
        end
    end
